# Copy to `api/.env` when running the API outside Docker (nodemon from `api/`).
# Docker Compose loads Zoom + other vars from the project root `.env` — see `../.env.example`.
#
# `api/config/load-env.js` loads in order: API_ENV_FILE (if set), then this file, then repo root `.env`, then cwd `.env`.
# Variables already set (e.g. by Docker) are never overwritten.

# Zoom Meeting SDK (embedded telemedicine video)
# ZOOM_CLIENT_ID=
# ZOOM_CLIENT_SECRET=

# Aliases (same values as Client ID / Client Secret from Zoom Marketplace)
# ZOOM_MEETING_SDK_KEY=
# ZOOM_MEETING_SDK_SECRET=
